      "text": "行 2: 关闭AUPC scpc 关aupc aupc关scpc | set-if-aupc:disable@bid=4..."
    },
    {
      "id": "row3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 30,
