      "text": "保存"
    },
    {
      "id": "cancelbtn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 300,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 100,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "取消"
    },
    {
      "id": "legend",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## 交互流程\n\n**打开编辑器**\nSessionControl 点击\"编辑规则\"\n→ 加载 _ruleItems\n\n**保存**\n→ DialogResult = true\n→ Rules.ToList()\n→ SaveRules(rules.json)\n→ 刷新 _intentRules\n\n**过滤**\n搜索框 TextChanged\n→ 绑定 filteredView\n→ DataGrid 显示子集\n\n**排序**\n拖拽后更新 ObservableCollection\n顺序保持到文件"
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "id": "e01",
